<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٩ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" شَرَفُ الْمُؤْمِنِ فِي قِيَامِهِ بِاللَّيْلِ، وَعِزُّهُ اسْتِغْنَاؤُهُ عَنِ النَّاسِ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨٠ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> الْفَقْرُ سَوَادُ الْوَجْهِ فِي الدَّارَيْنِ <span style="color:#950000">".<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٨١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> " حُبُّ الْوَطَنِ مِنَ الإِيمَانِ ".<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>